videos.headline: Hot-potato football gets WVU a first down
videos.description: West Virginia's Skyler Howard throws to Shelton Gibson who gets popped and loses the ball, it goes to Arizona State's Salamo Fiso but he only bats it up into the air to Daikiel Shorts for an unconventional 18 yard gain for the Mountaineers.
